OL,3,CPopular flights up to 30% more
OL,4,Cexpensive from Guernsey than Jersey
OL,6,FFlights taking off from Guernsey can
OL,7,Fcost islanders up to 30% more than the
OL,8,Fequivalent journey from Jersey or the
OL,9,FIsle of Man, an independent report has
OL,10,Fconcluded.
OL,12,FThe review by Frontier Economics looks
OL,13,Fat the state of air connectivity,
OL,14,Faffordability, and reliability with
OL,15,Fdata from 2010 to 2024.
OL,17,FTheir research found that Guernsey
OL,18,Fflights on the most popular routes can
OL,19,Fcost between 15% to 30% more than
OL,20,Fthose from the other Crown
OL,21,FDependencies.
