OL,4,Cexpensive from Guernsey than Jersey
OL,6,FSome of that price difference can be
OL,7,Fexplained by factors such as different
OL,8,Fairport charges, demand, aircraft size
OL,9,Fand potential subsidies offered by the
OL,10,Fother islands that are not included in
OL,11,Fthis analysis.
OL,13,FHowever, the report says the data
OL,14,Fstill supports the view that Guernsey
OL,15,Fshould consider further measures to
OL,16,Fimprove the affordability of flights.
