OL,4,Cexpensive from Guernsey than Jersey
OL,6,FOverall, Guernsey air travel was found
OL,7,Fto be similarly reliable to Jersey and
OL,8,Fthe Isle of Man pre-2024, although it
OL,9,Fworsens on some lower-frequency routes
OL,10,Fsuch as Birmingham, Manchester, Leeds
OL,11,Fand Exeter and last year the island's
OL,12,Fperformance dropped considerably.
OL,14,FDeputy Neil Inder, President of
OL,15,FGuernsey's Economic Development
OL,16,FCommittee, says: "Significant concerns
OL,17,Fwere raised by the public, the
OL,18,Fbusiness community and the travelling
OL,19,Fpublic and I was particularly keen to
OL,20,Fensure that my Committee got an
OL,21,Findependent view.
