OL,3,CPopular flights up to 30% more
OL,4,Cexpensive from Guernsey than Jersey
OL,6,F"Despite the positive market
OL,7,Fconfidence we are seeing, passenger
OL,8,Ffigures are still recovering from pre-
OL,9,Fpandemic levels and affordability of
OL,10,Fairfares is an area of concern where
OL,11,Fimprovement is needed.
OL,13,F"The Committee's view is that, as
OL,14,FState-owned assets, both Aurigny and
OL,15,FGuernsey Airport should be used as
OL,16,Feconomic enablers; price and
OL,17,Faffordability are a factor in
OL,18,Fbusinesses making decisions to use the
OL,19,Fisland as a base."
